        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Linear Generator Parity Act</b></p> <p>This bill modifies the tax credit for investments in energy property to make qualified fuel cell property (certain fuel cell power plants) that uses an electromechanical process eligible for the credit.</p>]]>
